Name: CTAP1_ERR_INVALID_COMMAND
Description: The command is not a valid CTAP command.

Name: CTAP1_ERR_INVALID_PARAMETER
Description: The command included an invalid parameter.

Name: CTAP1_ERR_INVALID_CHANNEL
Description: Command not allowed on this cid.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_LIMIT_EXCEEDED
Description: Limit for number of items exceeded.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_CREDENTIAL_EXCLUDED
Description: Valid credential found in the exclude list.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIAL
Description: Credential not valid for the authenticator.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_USER_ACTION_PENDING
Description: Authentication is waiting for user interaction.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_OPERATION_PENDING
Description: Processing, lengthy operation is in progress.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_UNSUPPORTED_ALGORITHM
Description: Authenticator does not support requested algorithm.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_NOT_BUSY
Description: Authenticator cannot cancel as it is not busy.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_INVALID_OPTION
Description: Not a valid option for current operation.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_NOT_ALLOWED
Description: Continuation command, such as, authenticatorGetNextAssertion not allowed.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_PIN_AUTH_BLOCKED
Description: PIN authentication,pinAuth, blocked. Requires power recycle to reset.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_PIN_REQUIRED
Description: PIN is required for the selected operation.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_PIN_POLICY_VIOLATION
Description: PIN policy violation. Currently only enforces minimum length.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_REQUEST_TOO_LARGE
Description: Authenticator cannot handle this request due to memory constraints.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_ACTION_TIMEOUT
Description: The current operation has timed out.

Name: CTAP2_ERR_UP_REQUIRED
Description: User presence is required for the requested operation.
